# Page Templates

## Landing Page

### Structure
```
Header/Navigation
Hero Section
Social Proof (logos, testimonials)
Features Section
How It Works
Pricing (optional)
FAQ
CTA Section
Footer
```

### Hero Section
- **Headline**: Clear value proposition (< 60 chars)
- **Subheadline**: Supporting detail (2-3 sentences)
- **Primary CTA**: Prominent button
- **Secondary CTA**: Optional alternative action
- **Visual**: Image, illustration, or product screenshot
- **Height**: 60-80vh (viewport height)

### Features Section
- **Grid**: 2-4 columns (responsive)
- **Icon**: 24-48px per feature
- **Title**: 18-24px, semibold
- **Description**: 2-3 sentences
- **Spacing**: 48-64px between features

### Social Proof
- **Customer logos**: 4-8 logos, grayscale
- **Testimonials**: 2-3 quotes with photos
- **Stats**: Key metrics (users, revenue, etc.)

### CTA Section
- **Headline**: Action-oriented
- **Button**: Large, prominent
- **Background**: Contrasting color or gradient
- **Padding**: Generous (64-96px vertical)

## Dashboard Page

### Layout
```
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│ Header (logo, search, profile)  │
├────────┬────────────────────────┤
│ Side   │ Main Content           │
│ Nav    │ ┌────────────────────┐ │
│        │ │ Page Header        │ │
│        │ ├────────────────────┤ │
│        │ │ Metrics/Stats      │ │
│        │ ├────────────────────┤ │
│        │ │ Data Table         │ │
│        │ └────────────────────┘ │
└────────┴────────────────────────┘
```

### Components
- **Sidebar**: 240-280px, collapsible
- **Header**: 56-64px height, sticky
- **Page Title**: H1, with actions
- **Metrics Cards**: 2-4 columns, key stats
- **Data Table**: Sortable, paginated
- **Filters**: Above table or in sidebar
- **Charts**: Responsive, labeled

### Metrics Cards
```html
<div class="metrics-grid">
  <div class="metric-card">
    <div class="metric-label">Total Users</div>
    <div class="metric-value">12,345</div>
    <div class="metric-change">+12.5%</div>
  </div>
</div>
```

## Settings Page

### Layout
- **Sidebar**: Category navigation
- **Main**: Form sections
- **Sticky Save**: Save button always visible

### Sections
- Profile Settings
- Account Settings
- Notifications
- Privacy & Security
- Billing (if applicable)

### Form Pattern
```html
<section class="settings-section">
  <h2>Section Title</h2>
  <p>Section description</p>
  
  <div class="form-field">
    <label>Setting Name</label>
    <input type="text">
    <span class="help-text">Help text</span>
  </div>
  
  <button>Save Changes</button>
</section>
```

## Authentication Pages

### Login
```
┌─────────────────┐
│ Logo            │
│                 │
│ Welcome Back    │
│                 │
│ Email           │
│ Password        │
│ [Remember Me]   │
│                 │
│ [Sign In]       │
│                 │
│ Forgot Password?│
│ Sign Up         │
└─────────────────┘
```

### Sign Up
- Similar to login
- Additional fields (name, etc.)
- Password requirements
- Terms acceptance
- Social sign-up options

## Error Pages

### 404 Not Found
- **Headline**: "Page Not Found"
- **Description**: Helpful message
- **Search**: Optional search box
- **Links**: Popular pages
- **CTA**: Back to home

### 500 Server Error
- **Headline**: "Something Went Wrong"
- **Description**: Apologetic message
- **Action**: Retry button
- **Support**: Contact link

## Blog/Article Page

### Structure
```
Header
Article Header
  - Title (H1)
  - Meta (author, date, reading time)
  - Featured Image
Article Body
  - Headings (H2, H3)
  - Paragraphs (max-width: 65ch)
  - Images
  - Code blocks
  - Quotes
Related Articles
Comments (optional)
Footer
```

### Typography
- **Title**: 32-48px, bold
- **Body**: 16-18px, line-height 1.6
- **Max width**: 65ch (characters)
- **Paragraph spacing**: 1em

## Profile Page

### Header
- **Avatar**: 80-120px
- **Name**: H1
- **Bio**: 2-3 sentences
- **Stats**: Followers, following, posts
- **Actions**: Follow, message, edit

### Content
- **Tabs**: Posts, About, Activity
- **Grid**: 2-3 columns for posts
- **List**: Activity feed

## Search Results Page

### Layout
```
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│ Search Bar                      │
├─────────┬───────────────────────┤
│ Filters │ Results               │
│         │ ┌───────────────────┐ │
│ Type    │ │ Result 1          │ │
│ Date    │ ├───────────────────┤ │
│ Sort    │ │ Result 2          │ │
│         │ └───────────────────┘ │
│         │ Pagination            │
└─────────┴───────────────────────┘
```

### Result Item
- **Title**: H3, link
- **Snippet**: 2-3 lines
- **Meta**: Date, author, category
- **Thumbnail**: Optional image

## Checkout/Payment Page

### Steps
1. Cart Review
2. Shipping Information
3. Payment Method
4. Order Confirmation

### Layout
- **Main**: Form (left, 60%)
- **Sidebar**: Order summary (right, 40%)
- **Progress**: Step indicator at top
- **Security**: Trust badges

## Best Practices

### Do
- Use consistent page structure
- Include breadcrumbs for deep pages
- Show loading states
- Handle empty states
- Provide clear navigation
- Use semantic landmarks
- Optimize for SEO (title, meta, headings)
- Make CTAs obvious
- Test on mobile

### Don't
- Bury important content
- Use too many columns
- Ignore mobile layout
- Forget page titles
- Skip loading indicators
- Use unclear navigation
- Make users scroll excessively
- Hide important actions
